Review Presentation
• Will discuss the role of GitHib and ZenHub for creating a backlog and managing the kanban

Work in GitHub and ZenHub
• Create general backlog of stories 
• Take one group of stories in an epic and create acceptance criteria for each story
• Divide stories into
- – Icebox (unprioritized backlog)
- – Cool List (low priority)
- – Warm List (upcoming and higher priority)
- – Hot List (do now)

- – - – - – - – - – - – - – - – - – - 
Class
- review rough backlog and acceptance criteria
- review prioritized backlog

