Review Presentation
- will discuss the differences in estimating using planning poker vs. t-shirt sizing

To do before class
• define what each t-shirt size means to the team in terms of complexity and effort
• make sure that each larger size is relatively estimated 
• have the warm and hot list stories sized
• Use https://www.planningpoker.com to help

- – - – - – - – - – - – - – - – - – - 
Class
• Review team definitions of the meaning of each t-shirt size 
• Review the warm and hot list stories sized

